=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex7 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with fm_or_inharmonic oscillator character around 620 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 620.4579
  harmonic_decay_rate: -10.3345
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5011
  pitch_clarity: 24.7326
  inharmonicity: 0.1296
  type: fm_or_inharmonic
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -4.7333
  resonance_freq: 581.3965

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: UGen Example 7
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/UGen.html
// Tags: UGen, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 7 ---
{ SinOsc.ar(SinOsc.ar(0.3).curverange(440, 660, -3), 0, 0.5) * 0.1 }.play;
